                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-red-600 mr-2">‚úó</span>
                  <span>Major updates require native app store release (1.0.0 ‚Üí 2.0.0)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-yellow-600 mr-2">‚ö†</span>
